      "writtenOn": "2017-10-27T19:03:55Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Seems feasible, but I can\u0027t think of a situation where we\u0027d need more than one of those values, and it seems like it would add a lot of complication.  In any situation where we\u0027d want a secondary display of the contained datetime we could just use a human-date-sk with any of the output formats.",
